UNO Deep Fryer offers all the features you could need from a deep fryer for home use. Not only is it easy to use but with a variety of features it also operates safely - and safety is important for any kitchen. It has a high capacity which lets you cook up to 2.2 lbs of food at one time, making this fryer great for feeding your family and guests. Easy to clean If you're hesitating because you think cleaning might be a problem, then let this fryer ease your concerns. The lid and basket are dishwasher safe, which makes for quick and easy cleaning. Take a big chunk of the workload off with this well designed fryer. Multiple temperature settings Do you need to dial in on a specific temperature for a certain type of food? Not a problem! This fryer has multiple temperature settings, letting you cook your food exactly the way you want it. You'll get the results you're looking for consistently and easily thanks to this feature. Ready light Setup and preparation is easy with the ready light feature. It lets you know when the fryer has reached the set temperature so you can get right to cooking. It saves you the trouble of having to do any guesswork or hassle with other ways to check the oil temperature.1.8 liter oil capacity2.2 lbs food capacity Easy to clean Dishwasher safe components Multiple temperature settings1200 watts2.2lbs food capacity Don't leave anyone wanting! With this deep fryer, you can cook up to 2.2 lbs of food at a time, allowing you to make plenty to go around. And since it's easy to use as well as safe, serving a whole party of people is not a problem. Easy and safe to use with multiple features making it safe and easy to use, this deep fryer is ideal for any home. It has automatic opening, handles for easy carrying, a cool touch housing, and a quick store handle. These feature will help protect you from any accidents so you can use it for what it's meant for - cooking delicious food.
